    <!-- MASTER THESIS PAGE -->
    <div id="page-thesis" class="category-detail hidden">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="back-button" onclick="showPage('home')">‚Üê <span data-en="Back to Home" data-de="Zur√ºck zur Startseite">Back to Home</span></a>
            <h1 class="section-title">üìù <span data-en="Master Thesis Tools" data-de="Masterarbeit Tools">Master Thesis Tools</span></h1>
            <p style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-muted);"
               data-en="Find company collaboration opportunities for research-focused thesis projects with real-world impact."
               data-de="Finden Sie Unternehmenskooperationen f√ºr forschungsorientierte Abschlussarbeiten.">
                Find company collaboration opportunities for research-focused thesis projects with real-world impact.
            </p>

            <div class="prompts-header">
                <h2 class="section-title" style="margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem;">ü§ñ <span data-en="AI Prompts Library" data-de="KI-Prompts Bibliothek">AI Prompts Library</span></h2>
                <button class="prompts-toggle-btn" onclick="togglePrompts('thesis-prompts', this)">
                    <span data-en="View AI Prompts" data-de="KI-Prompts Anzeigen">View AI Prompts</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <div id="thesis-prompts" class="prompts-container">
                <div class="prompt-category">
                    <h3>üîç 1. Finding Companies for Master's Thesis + Job</h3>
                    <div class="prompt-item">
                        <h4>üéØ Company Discovery Prompt</h4>
                        <div class="prompt-content">
                            <strong>Background Information to Provide:</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Degree and specialization</li>
                                <li>University and thesis requirements</li>
                                <li>Preferred industry or function</li>
                                <li>Location preference (Germany/city)</li>
                                <li>Working student or part-time job status</li>
                            </ul>
                            <strong>Copy-Paste Prompt:</strong>
                            <p>"I am studying [degree] at [university] with specialization in [area]. My thesis must meet [requirements]. I prefer [industry] in [location]. I am [currently working/looking for] a working student position. Please:

1. Identify types of companies in Germany that are open to Master's thesis collaborations in my field
2. Suggest specific departments (R&D, Strategy, Operations, etc.) where Master's theses are commonly offered
3. Explain the key differences between corporate, SME (Mittelstand), and startup thesis collaborations
4. List platforms, portals, and networking strategies to find thesis-friendly companies
5. Advise how early I should approach companies before my thesis officially starts (e.g., 3 months, 6 months)"</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="prompt-category">
                    <h3>üíº 2. Convincing a Company to Allow Thesis With a Job</h3>
                    <div class="prompt-item">
                        <h4>üéØ Company Pitch Prompt</h4>
                        <div class="prompt-content">
                            <strong>Background Information to Provide:</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Current or target company</li>
                                <li>Working student or part-time role details</li>
                                <li>Thesis duration and university requirements</li>
                                <li>Proposed general thesis area</li>
                            </ul>
                            <strong>Copy-Paste Prompt:</strong>
                            <p>"I am working/applying at [company] as a [role]. I need to complete my Master's thesis over [duration]. My thesis topic relates to [general area]. Please:

1. Help me frame my Master's thesis as a valuable business solution, not just an academic requirement or burden
2. Draft a convincing, professional email to HR or my hiring manager proposing the thesis collaboration
3. Address common concerns about time commitment, workload balance, and productivity
4. Proactively address confidentiality, data access, and intellectual property (IP) concerns
5. Explain how company supervision can be kept low-effort and non-intrusive for busy managers"</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

