1. Create a detailed, actionable 30-60-90 day onboarding plan tailored to my role and German workplace culture
2. Explain realistic performance expectations for new hires in Germany during probation periods
3. Outline German workplace communication norms and feedback culture I should be aware of
4. Highlight cultural dos and don'ts in German professional environments
5. Help me build credibility and trust with my team and manager in the first three months"</p>
